title: Church Complaints, Brittney Griner, Mike Tyson Hulu, Husband Said Wrong Name and more.
itunes:title: Church Complaints, Brittney Griner, Mike Tyson Hulu, Husband Said Wrong Name and more.
description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride!  Why are we here really?  Pastor Motown sets the rules for members over 60 years old in Church Complaints.  The CLO got his hands full with a potential husband hopper.  Robert lost most of his commissary money just because.  The Baddest Man on The Planet ain't too happy with Hulu!  Carla was stuntin' with a member of the Knowles family and Steve gave us the highlights of Invest Fest.  Your favorite play cousin touches on who will not be in the Super Bowl.  Kids, drunks, and patients coming off anesthesia tell the truth!  Congrats to Khloe and Tristan on their second baby despite not touching each other.  The slickness was on full display in this round of Would You Rather.  Today in Closing Remarks, Steve straight up says it, "Start your plan."

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
